item.description:
This is basicaly a redo of the cancelled meeting from the 14th

focus will be mainly on our winter seabird visitors and also maybe some scenics of the coastline

High tide is at about 7:30 in the morning so the prime conditions will be early for the feeding ducks

as before I will determine final meeting place when all of the reports of what is happening in the area are looked over

This is going to happen on Thanksgiving weekend so be sure you are free to make it before you rsvp

It is not fair to take up a spot that someone else may really want just because you think you might be able to go

Please make sure of your schedule before saying yes

thanks

John
item.how_to_find_us: final spot will be emailed to attendees
